longBusinessSummary: Water Oasis Group Limited, an investment holding company, engages in the operation of beauty services outlets and distribution of skincare products in Hong Kong, Macau, and the People's Republic of China. It operates through Product and Service segments. The company provides general, specialist, dental, spa, salon, medical beauty, and aesthetic services to high-end, mid-range, and mass-market consumer sectors for men and women through its outlets, including Oasis Beauty, Oasis Medical, Oasis Spa, and Oasis Dental centres, as well as Oasis Beauty stores and salons, Oasis Hair spas, spa ph+, Oasis Mom, Oasis Florist, AesMedic Clinic, Glycel, Eurobeauté, and Erno Laszlo. It also manufactures and sells its skincare products comprising cellular therapy and anti-aging products offered under Glycel brand, home-based skincare solutions under Eurobeauté brand, and medical beauty products under DermaSynergy brand, as well as distributes HABA, Erno Laszlo and H2O+ branded skincare and beauty products. In addition, the company operates an online florist shops and beauty schools; holds trademarks; and provides management services. Further, it is involved in the online sale of skincare products; provision of beauty equipment; and property holding business, as well as produces and sells cold pressed fruit juice and healing tea. As of September 30, 2022, the company operated a total of 15 Oasis Beauty centers, 4 Oasis Hair Spas, and 2 Oasis Homme centers in Hong Kong; and 3 self-managed Oasis Beauty centers in Beijing, the People's Republic of China. Water Oasis Group Limited was founded in 1998 and is headquartered in Causeway Bay, Hong Kong.
